{
  "stem": "12756.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe they let you, they accept you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, and I went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and they don't let me through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was some-- before I went to them, they don't stay always.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The partisan, they watch them, you know, all around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They ask me what-- what I want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I say, I've been a butcher for trade, in my trade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I could help get meat for the partisan and make some meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, with-- like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They brought me over to the commander, to the sergeant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See I don't remember anything because I-- I don't remember these days, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's another one day [? there for then. ?] You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So already it was, what-- 40 year, 50 years, or 60.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, he-- he brought us over there, and they asked me-- what you know about-- about meat?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say I know take out the skin and cut them and do everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They accept me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was this a Jewish partisan group?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was about three or four, five of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not the all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we was in different groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in the group by the cattle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other-- other ones used to go and fight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Between them and the other ways, everybody in some-- they-- they was-- when they was walking, they walking for five miles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So many horses and so many partisans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe was 2,000 partisans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we was walking, the-- the Germans know-- thought we 20 people, partisans walking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we was just about maybe 1,000.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was women, too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No children.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kovpak.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's [? the cell. ?] That's the main leader, the-- the general.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
